javax.jcr

Interface Credentials

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuestCredentials, SimpleCredentials

    public interface Credentials
extends Serializable
    Interface for all credentials that may be passed to the Repository.login(Credentials credentials, String workspaceName) method. Serves as a marker interface that all repositories must implement when providing a credentials class. See SimpleCredentials and GuestCredentials for examples of such a class.
